-- ft.page: Featured components

-- ftd.column:
margin-top: -44
width: fill

-- ft.markdown:

We have designed and developed below components using `FTD` and `FPM` package. 
Use them for writing e-books, blogs, web technical documentation etc. 

These components can be used inside your personal web sites or organizational static 
web sites developed using `FPM` package.

